# iChat - Real-time Chat Application

A simple real-time chat web application built with Socket.IO.

## Features

- Real-time message exchange
- "Typing..." indicator
- Connected users counter
- Sound notifications
- Responsive design

## Technologies

- Node.js
- Express.js
- Socket.IO
- HTML/CSS/JavaScript
- Moment.js

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd websockets
```

2. Install dependencies:
```bash
npm install
```

3. Start the server:
```bash
npm run dev
```

4. Open your browser: http://localhost:4000

